                                                                                  <h4>Averting dangerous climate change</h4>
                                        <div class="description-container">
                      <p>We’re pushing the UK for the strongest ambition and measures to help tackle the climate emergency.<br><br>We’re doing this by influencing government policies in the UK, working with the finance and investment sector to help it align with 1.5°C targets, and identifying and promoting nature-based solutions to the climate crisis.</p>
                                                                      <div class="find-out-more-container">
                          <a href="/what-we-do/climate-change-and-energy">
                                                          Our work on climate
                                                        <i class="fa fa-arrow-right"></i>
                          </a>
                        </div>
                                          </div>
                  </figcaption>
                </figure>
              </li>
                                                                    <li class="splide__slide">
                <figure>
                  <img src="https://www.wwf.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/square_xs/public/2023-02/Medium_WW2102089.jpg?h=10d202d3&amp;itok=0qALefqb"
                       srcset="https://www.wwf.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/square_xs/public/2023-02/Medium_WW2102089.jpg?h=10d202d3&amp;itok=0qALefqb 320w,
