                    <a href="#" class="show show-text">More <i class="show fa fa-arrow-circle-o-up"></i></a>
                    <a href="#" class="hide hide-text">Close <i class="hide fa fa-close"></i></a>

                                                                                  <h4>Restoring habitats and species</h4>
                                        <div class="description-container">
                      <p>We’re working to halt the loss of habitats and restore natural-life support systems for people and species in some of the world’s most biodiverse places.<br><br>We’re doing this through large-scale landscapes and seascapes programmes, particularly in the Amazon, east Africa, Asia and the UK, while supporting communities and Indigenous peoples to exercise their rights.</p>
                                                                      <div class="find-out-more-container">
                          <a href="/learn/wildlife">
                                                          Our work with Wildlife
                                                        <i class="fa fa-arrow-right"></i>
                          </a>
                        </div>
                                          </div>
                  </figcaption>
                </figure>
              </li>
                                                                    <li class="splide__slide">
                <figure>
                  <img src="https://www.wwf.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/square_xs/public/2023-02/Medium_WW1218888.jpg?h=10d202d3&amp;itok=JFoK6ub2"
                       srcset="https://www.wwf.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/square_xs/public/2023-02/Medium_WW1218888.jpg?h=10d202d3&amp;itok=JFoK6ub2 320w,
                         https://www.wwf.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/square_s/public/2023-02/Medium_WW1218888.jpg?h=10d202d3&amp;itok=iXvjUPB8 640w,
                         https://www.wwf.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/square_m_new/public/2023-02/Medium_WW1218888.jpg?h=10d202d3&amp;itok=2B1JRvMj 768w,
                         https://www.wwf.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/square_l/public/2023-02/Medium_WW1218888.jpg?h=10d202d3&amp;itok=p1FlRdjP 1024w,
                         https://www.wwf.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/square_l/public/2023-02/Medium_WW1218888.jpg?h=10d202d3&amp;itok=p1FlRdjP 1200w,
