                    <a href="#" class="show show-text">More <i class="show fa fa-arrow-circle-o-up"></i></a>
                    <a href="#" class="hide hide-text">Close <i class="hide fa fa-close"></i></a>

                                                                                  <h4>Creating a sustainable food system</h4>
                                        <div class="description-container">
                      <p>We can’t bring our world back to life without creating a more sustainable food system. That’s why we’re working to reform it – to halt nature loss and ensure the UK leads a global transformation to sustainable food production and consumption.<br><br>We’re doing this by working with retailers and others, so they invest in nature’s restoration and pressing for policies to remove deforestation from our agricultural supply chains.</p>
                                                                      <div class="find-out-more-container">
                          <a href="/food">
                                                          Our work on food systems
                                                        <i class="fa fa-arrow-right"></i>
                          </a>
                        </div>
                                          </div>
                  </figcaption>
                </figure>
              </li>
                      </ul>
        </div>
