        <div class="media-block__info__content">
            <h3>Partnerships</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="media-block__text-slice">
          Through strategic partnerships with companies, we can help them reduce their environmental impact and advocate together to move whole sectors towards better ways of doing business.

        </div>
    </div>
    </div>
        <div class="media-block__btn_container">
