    </a>
    <div class="media-block__base media-block__info media-block__info--black-background ">
        <div class="media-block__info__content">
            <h3>Our Ambassadors</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="media-block__text-slice">
          WWF-UK&#039;s Council of ambassadors is a distinguished and influential group of senior volunteers. Members have achieved a significant profile in their profession and/or field of interest or expertise and are committed to WWF&#039;s mission.

        </div>
    </div>
    </div>
        <div class="media-block__btn_container">
      <a href="/who-we-are/council-of-ambassadors" class="btn links-block-btn " >Our work with ambassadors</a>
