  <div class="article_wrapper">
    
      <center><h3>UK offices</h3></center>

  </div>
</section>

  <div class="links_block--wrap paragraph-container">
    <div id="our-offices" class="grid_wrapper content flex_content column-d-3 column-t-2 column-m-1">
                  <div class="grid grid-cols-wwf-3">
        
<div id="uk-headquarters" class="media-block background-black">
  <div class="media-block__wrapper">
    <a href="https://www.wwf.org.uk/get-involved/living-planet-centre" >
        <img alt="UK Headquarters" src="/sites/default/files/styles/links_block_call_to_action/public/2017-07/WWF-UK%20Living%20Planet%20Centre%20108.jpg?h=c9f93661&amp;itok=CtRT8obC" class="media-block__image media-block__image--medium" />
    </a>
    <div class="media-block__base media-block__info media-block__info--black-background ">
        <div class="media-block__info__content">
            <h3>UK Headquarters</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="media-block__text-slice">
          We’re proud to introduce you to the home of WWF-UK. The Living Planet Centre is not only the heart of the charity, but one of the greenest buildings in the UK. It shows that through the smart use of design, materials and technology, it’s possible to create a state-of-the-art building with minimal environmental impact.

        </div>
    </div>
    </div>
        <div class="media-block__btn_container">
      <a href="https://www.wwf.org.uk/get-involved/living-planet-centre" class="btn links-block-btn " >Living Planet Centre</a>
    </div>
    </div>

<div id="wwf-scotland" class="media-block background-black">
  <div class="media-block__wrapper">
    <a href="https://www.wwf.org.uk/scotland" >
        <img alt="WWF-Scotland" src="/sites/default/files/styles/links_block_call_to_action_medium/public/2022-09/Scotland%20autumn%20credit%20northlightimages_3.jpg?h=381337e4&amp;itok=edQBbCCF" class="media-block__image media-block__image--medium" />
    </a>
    <div class="media-block__base media-block__info media-block__info--black-background ">
        <div class="media-block__info__content">
            <h3>WWF-Scotland</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="media-block__text-slice">
          WWF-Scotland is working for a cleaner, fairer, flourishing environment where people and nature thrive. To achieve this, we’re tackling the main causes of nature loss and climate change, including land use, our food systems and energy emissions.

        </div>
    </div>
    </div>
        <div class="media-block__btn_container">
      <a href="https://www.wwf.org.uk/scotland" class="btn links-block-btn " >Our work in Scotland</a>
    </div>
    </div>

<div id="wwf-cymru" class="media-block background-black">
  <div class="media-block__wrapper">
    <a href="https://www.wwf.org.uk/who-we-are/wales" >
        <img alt="WWF-Cymru" src="/sites/default/files/styles/links_block_call_to_action_medium/public/2022-11/DSC_7290.jpg?h=ba809569&amp;itok=OYPw-I2m" class="media-block__image media-block__image--medium" />
    </a>
    <div class="media-block__base media-block__info media-block__info--black-background ">
        <div class="media-block__info__content">
            <h3>WWF-Cymru</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="media-block__text-slice">
          WWF-Cymru will nurture partnerships that equip and inspire people, communities and other leaders in the co-creation of transformational and just solutions that tackle the climate crisis and restore nature.

        </div>
    </div>
    </div>
        <div class="media-block__btn_container">
      <a href="https://www.wwf.org.uk/who-we-are/wales" class="btn links-block-btn " >Our work in Cymru</a>
    </div>
